      "title": "Grand Bible Seminar (July 13-19)",
      "body": "The July Grand Bible Seminar will be held at our church with speaker p.Chongkyung Park.\n- July 13-18 (Mon-Sat): 8 PM\n- July 19 (Sun): 11 AM\nPlease invite your friends and family to this special event."
    },
    {
      "title": "July New Believer Training: Holy (July 19th)",
      "body": "It is a time to learn and fellowship together about what is essential for Christian life. We look forward to your involvement. (inquiry: b.Andrew)"
    },
    {
      "title": "Service in church",
      "body": "If you have been saved for over a year and would like to participate in service work at the church, please contact our pastor."
    },
    {
      "title": "Consultation and Visitation",
      "body": "If you need evangelism counseling, Christian life counseling, or visitation, please contact the pastor."
    },
    {
      "title": "Church Clean Management: Beverage and Food Waste Disposal",
      "body": "Please pay attention to the disposal of beverage and food waste for a pleasant environment in the church.\n- Please dispose of remaining beverages and ice separately before throwing away the cups in the trash can. Also, please be mindful to minimize food waste. If you need to dispose of food waste, please seal it tightly to prevent exposure."
    }
